Fang Zhuoying buat dengan baik.

253
00:14:22,760 --> 00:14:24,559
Dia sudah berakar umbi
di Puak Kanan Hu Ku,

254
00:14:24,840 --> 00:14:26,440
jadi pasti akan
mempunyai pencapaian kelak.

255
00:14:27,919 --> 00:14:28,880
Kali ini,

256
00:14:29,640 --> 00:14:31,599
awak suruh Zhuoying
buat-buat membunuh beta

257
00:14:31,919 --> 00:14:33,840
dan biar Fang Haishi pergi memburu dia.

258
00:14:34,960 --> 00:14:36,000
Awak dah pasti bahawa

259
00:14:36,599 --> 00:14:38,080
Fang Haishi akan melepaskan dia.

260
00:14:41,599 --> 00:14:42,880
Awak berwaspada langkah demi langkah

261
00:14:43,039 --> 00:14:44,960
dan berjaya menghentikan
kritikan orang ramai.

262
00:14:46,400 --> 00:14:47,320
Namun, pernahkah awak memikirkan

263
00:14:47,440 --> 00:14:48,239
Fang Haishi?

264
00:14:48,960 --> 00:14:50,000
Beta pun rasa

265
00:14:50,960 --> 00:14:52,119
awak terlalu kejam

266
00:14:52,640 --> 00:14:53,880
terhadap dia.

267
00:14:54,359 --> 00:14:55,960
Patutlah dia enggan pulang.

268
00:14:59,880 --> 00:15:00,880
Baik, jangan cakap ini.

269
00:15:01,119 --> 00:15:01,479
Mari.

270
00:15:01,640 --> 00:15:02,320
Tengok ini.

271
00:15:03,440 --> 00:15:04,080
Macam mana?

272
00:15:04,799 --> 00:15:05,840
Adakah kemahirannya lemah sikit

273
00:15:06,000 --> 00:15:07,239
daripada kemahiran Zhe Liu?

274
00:15:08,440 --> 00:15:09,599
Beta nak...

275
00:15:12,679 --> 00:15:14,559
Beta berniat

276
00:15:15,359 --> 00:15:16,880
untuk menabalkan Gundik Shu Rong
sebagai pewaris maharani.

277
00:15:19,760 --> 00:15:21,760
Dia datang dari jauh ke Kota Tianqi.

278
00:15:22,559 --> 00:15:24,400
Pada masa itu, beta membenci dia.

279
00:15:25,239 --> 00:15:26,320
Beta tak kurniakan
majlis perkahwinan yang bagus

280
00:15:26,320 --> 00:15:27,200
kepada dia pun.

281
00:15:28,479 --> 00:15:29,840
Tibalah masa untuk berhasil.

282
00:15:31,679 --> 00:15:32,119
Bagus juga.

283
00:15:37,479 --> 00:15:38,280
Macam mana dengan awak?

284
00:15:39,919 --> 00:15:40,520
Bilakah awak

285
00:15:40,679 --> 00:15:41,880
sudi melepaskan masa lalu

286
00:15:42,640 --> 00:15:43,880
dan memulakan kehidupan baharu?

287
00:15:45,080 --> 00:15:46,239
Setelah segala-gala ditentukan,

288
00:15:46,919 --> 00:15:48,080
patik mempunyai satu permintaan.

289
00:15:49,000 --> 00:15:49,400
Cakaplah.

290
00:15:54,640 --> 00:15:55,840
Setelah dunia menjadi tenteram,

291
00:15:56,599 --> 00:15:58,479
Jianming berharap agar memutuskan

292
00:15:59,080 --> 00:16:00,200
ikatan patung Bai Xi dengan tuanku.

293
00:16:02,000 --> 00:16:03,440
Patik nak
meletakkan jawatan pentadbiran

294
00:16:03,599 --> 00:16:04,640
dan balik ke Liushang.

295
00:16:07,799 --> 00:16:09,159
Akhirnya, awak dah sedar.

296
00:16:09,520 --> 00:16:11,440
Awak dah sedar selepas banyak tahun ini.

297
00:16:12,880 --> 00:16:13,799
Dah lama beta bertitah bahawa

298
00:16:13,799 --> 00:16:14,320
hubungan kita tak patut diikat

299
00:16:14,440 --> 00:16:16,039
melalui patung Bai Xi.

300
00:16:18,679 --> 00:16:19,159
Jianming.

301
00:16:28,840 --> 00:16:29,440
Jianming,

302
00:16:30,479 --> 00:16:31,039
beta

303
00:16:31,840 --> 00:16:32,799
tak pernah berharap agar awak

304
00:16:32,840 --> 00:16:34,080
menjadi pembesar yang setia kepada beta.

305
00:16:35,039 --> 00:16:36,400
Beta cuma inginkan awak hidup senang

306
00:16:36,559 --> 00:16:37,640
dan gembira setiap hari.

307
00:16:41,200 --> 00:16:42,760
Ini akan tamat akhirnya.

308
00:16:43,960 --> 00:16:44,599
Tuanku,

309
00:16:45,479 --> 00:16:46,599
ia tak tamat.

310
00:16:47,280 --> 00:16:47,719
Ya.

311
00:16:49,559 --> 00:16:51,039
Ini permulaan baharu.

312
00:16:53,960 --> 00:16:54,479
Ah Xu,

313
00:16:55,840 --> 00:16:56,719
kata-kata awak betul.

314
00:16:58,080 --> 00:16:59,719
Memang ada seorang dalam hati saya.

315
00:17:02,599 --> 00:17:03,559
Saya berharap agar dapat

316
00:17:03,719 --> 00:17:04,760
merantau di seluruh dunia dengan dia

317
00:17:05,400 --> 00:17:06,359
dan hidup bersama dia
dalam hayat selebihnya.

318
00:17:06,880 --> 00:17:08,439
Saya nak tahu sekarang

319
00:17:08,640 --> 00:17:10,119
siapakah orang ini?

320
00:17:10,280 --> 00:17:10,959
Fang Jianming,

321
00:17:10,959 --> 00:17:11,800
dah lama awak merahsiakannya.

322
00:17:11,959 --> 00:17:13,560
Awak enggan beritahu saya hingga kini.

323
00:17:15,599 --> 00:17:17,199
Saya berselisih faham dengan dia.

324
00:17:18,160 --> 00:17:19,400
Selepas perselisihan ini selesai,

325
00:17:20,079 --> 00:17:21,400
dia sudi hidup bersama saya,

326
00:17:21,599 --> 00:17:22,520
saya pasti

327
00:17:22,800 --> 00:17:23,800
membawa dia untuk menemui awak.

328
00:17:27,119 --> 00:17:27,880
Siapakah

329
00:17:28,000 --> 00:17:29,199
wanita ini sebenarnya?

330
00:17:29,800 --> 00:17:31,319
Awak pun rasa tak yakin.

331
00:17:33,000 --> 00:17:33,800
Namun, betul juga.

332
00:17:35,040 --> 00:17:35,959
Jika

333
00:17:36,199 --> 00:17:37,760
tiada apa-apa yang istimewa,

334
00:17:38,079 --> 00:17:38,880
mustahil awak akan

335
00:17:39,040 --> 00:17:40,280
menyukai dia.

336
00:17:43,000 --> 00:17:45,560
Tanggal 18 bulan ini
ialah hari jadi Jichang.

337
00:17:45,560 --> 00:17:46,520
Beta dah menurunkan titah

338
00:17:46,719 --> 00:17:47,640
untuk menghayati

339
00:17:47,640 --> 00:17:49,479
anak helang ternakan Jichang
di Ladang Kuda Diraja Timur.

340
00:17:50,280 --> 00:17:51,599
Jika orang kesayangan awak

341
00:17:51,760 --> 00:17:53,040
sudi,

342
00:17:53,520 --> 00:17:54,640
bawa dia sekali.

343
00:17:55,040 --> 00:17:57,040
Biar beta tengok dia juga.

344
00:18:02,000 --> 00:18:02,520
Baik.

345
00:18:21,760 --> 00:18:23,040
Adakah Gundik Shu Rong penat?

346
00:18:23,160 --> 00:18:25,040
Apa kata patik
membantu puan untuk berehat?

347
00:18:26,439 --> 00:18:28,040
Entahlah kenapa saya amat penat

348
00:18:28,199 --> 00:18:29,599
kebelakangan ini.

349
00:18:30,760 --> 00:18:32,040
Pada waktu ini sebelum ini,

350
00:18:32,199 --> 00:18:33,760
saya masih bersemangat

351
00:18:34,160 --> 00:18:35,959
dan dapat membaca beberapa buku lagi.

352
00:18:37,359 --> 00:18:39,479
Wajah Gundik Shu Rong nampak baik.

353
00:18:39,959 --> 00:18:41,400
Puan tidak mengalami kesejukan
kebelakangan ini.

354
00:18:42,800 --> 00:18:44,520
Adakah Gundik Shu Rong rasa tak sihat?

355
00:18:44,680 --> 00:18:45,359
Apa kata jemput tabib diraja

356
00:18:45,479 --> 00:18:46,280
untuk datang periksa?

357
00:18:46,520 --> 00:18:47,239
Tak boleh.

358
00:18:48,880 --> 00:18:50,000
Tak boleh jemput tabib diraja.

359
00:18:51,000 --> 00:18:52,719
Macam mana jika ganggu baginda lagi?

360
00:18:53,800 --> 00:18:55,079
Baginda amat menyayangi Gundik Shu Rong

361
00:18:55,239 --> 00:18:56,119
sekarang.

362
00:18:56,199 --> 00:18:57,400
Jika benar-benar jemput tabib diraja,

363
00:18:57,560 --> 00:18:59,119
rasa-rasanya baginda yang resah dulu.

364
00:18:59,239 --> 00:19:00,119
Baginda akan terus berangkat tiba

365
00:19:00,160 --> 00:19:00,959
di Istana Yu'an lagi.

366
00:19:01,119 --> 00:19:02,119
Awak ini...

367
00:19:03,880 --> 00:19:05,160
Sup ginseng dihidangkan.

368
00:19:07,400 --> 00:19:08,560
Gundik Shu Rong, minum ketika panas.

369
00:19:11,280 --> 00:19:11,719
Siapa?

370
00:19:25,800 --> 00:19:27,000
Tak nampak orang.

371
00:19:27,319 --> 00:19:28,880
Rasa-rasanya,
dia berlari selepas buangnya.

372
00:19:42,119 --> 00:19:43,040
Gundik Shu Rong,

373
00:19:43,680 --> 00:19:44,719
bukankah ini...

374
00:19:47,800 --> 00:19:49,319
Azimat pelindung diri Suo Lan.

375
00:19:49,640 --> 00:19:51,079
Putera Mahkota Suo Lan.

376
00:20:02,640 --> 00:20:03,710
(Bunuh Maharaja Xu atau dia akan mati)
Bunuh Maharaja Xu.

377
00:20:04,040 --> 00:20:06,599
Jika tidak, pemilik aguk akan mati.

378
00:20:06,880 --> 00:20:08,239
Ini racun!

379
00:20:08,839 --> 00:20:10,359
Siapa yang begitu berani?

380
00:20:11,119 --> 00:20:11,839
Gundik Shu Rong,

381
00:20:12,160 --> 00:20:13,439
perlukah kita maklumkan baginda?

382
00:20:14,479 --> 00:20:15,479
Tak boleh!

383
00:20:16,119 --> 00:20:17,040
Ini azimat pelindung diri
yang sentiasa dibawa

384
00:20:17,199 --> 00:20:18,040
Putera Mahkota Suo Lan.

385
00:20:18,199 --> 00:20:18,959
Rasa-rasanya, orang biasa

386
00:20:19,079 --> 00:20:19,959
takkan dapatnya.

387
00:20:21,359 --> 00:20:22,079
Gundik Shu Rong,

388
00:20:22,400 --> 00:20:23,680
jika benar-benar berlaku sesuatu,

389
00:20:23,800 --> 00:20:24,839
Putera Mahkota Suo Lan...

390
00:20:25,839 --> 00:20:27,000
Dia adik puan,

391
00:20:27,160 --> 00:20:28,040
satu-satu putera

392
00:20:28,199 --> 00:20:29,520
dan bakal raja di Chola.

393
00:20:29,719 --> 00:20:30,959
Macam mana?

394
00:20:31,160 --> 00:20:31,920
Gundik Shu Rong,

395
00:20:32,079 --> 00:20:33,479
inginkah kita hantar khabar ke Chola?

396
00:20:34,199 --> 00:20:35,520
Usah cemas dulu.

397
00:20:39,400 --> 00:20:41,040
Biar saya fikir baik-baik.

398
00:20:49,599 --> 00:20:50,239
Gadis.

399
00:20:50,400 --> 00:20:51,959
Mari, bermain dengan saya.

400
00:20:53,680 --> 00:20:54,880
Cantiknya.

401
00:20:55,479 --> 00:20:57,199
Sampai giliran saya. Biar saya sentuh.

402
00:20:57,359 --> 00:20:57,839
Buat apa?

403
00:20:59,000 --> 00:20:59,640
Apa hal?

404
00:21:01,079 --> 00:21:02,400
Dia buat pengikut raja marah.

405
00:21:02,560 --> 00:21:04,119
Pengikut menghantar dia kepada kami.

406
00:21:04,560 --> 00:21:05,800
Budak yang membawa malang!

407
00:21:06,160 --> 00:21:07,199
Kebetulan pula, Putera Suo Lan

408
00:21:07,319 --> 00:21:07,959
nak memuja di kuil.

409
00:21:07,959 --> 00:21:08,760
Lekas berambus!

410
00:21:09,439 --> 00:21:10,680
Ya.

411
00:21:11,040 --> 00:21:11,800
Ayuh.

412
00:21:12,160 --> 00:21:12,640
Lekas pergi.

413
00:21:17,880 --> 00:21:18,839
Angkat kepala.

414
00:21:28,090 --> 00:21:29,470
(Istana Zichen)

415
00:21:29,479 --> 00:21:30,160
Tuanku,

416
00:21:30,880 --> 00:21:33,000
Puak Kiri dan Puak Kanan Hu Ku
di Negeri Han Utara

417
00:21:33,199 --> 00:21:34,239
saling menyerang.

418
00:21:34,520 --> 00:21:36,760
Puak Kanan makin mengalahkan Puak Kiri.

419
00:21:37,040 --> 00:21:38,640
Kedua-dua puak
sibuk menjaga hal sendiri,

420
00:21:38,800 --> 00:21:41,199
jadi tidak mengancam Genting Huangquan.

421
00:21:42,520 --> 00:21:43,400
Tuanku,

422
00:21:43,560 --> 00:21:44,839
pesisir pantai tenggara dan barat daya

423
00:21:45,040 --> 00:21:45,959
juga tenteram.

424
00:21:46,119 --> 00:21:49,040
Tiada apa-apa peperangan atau bencana.

425
00:22:00,119 --> 00:22:01,760
Ada warkah yang ingin disampaikan lagi?

426
00:22:06,160 --> 00:22:08,199
Patik tiada warkah.

427
00:22:11,520 --> 00:22:13,880
Bersurai!

428
00:22:16,520 --> 00:22:18,880
Selamat berangkat, tuanku.

429
00:22:21,000 --> 00:22:22,319
Bilakah awak nak

430
00:22:22,319 --> 00:22:24,000
balik menghadiri mesyuarat pagi?

431
00:22:25,119 --> 00:22:26,560
Tuanku,

432
00:22:26,560 --> 00:22:27,079
seketika masa lagi.

433
00:22:28,280 --> 00:22:29,160
Lekas balik.

434
00:22:29,640 --> 00:22:30,239
Tanpa awak,

435
00:22:31,280 --> 00:22:32,640
bosannya beta menghadiri mesyuarat.

436
00:22:33,920 --> 00:22:34,439
Oh, ya.

437
00:22:36,000 --> 00:22:37,239
Anak murid kesayangan awak, Fang Haishi

438
00:22:37,599 --> 00:22:39,680
kata bahawa dia melepaskan Fang Zhuoying
secara tak sengaja

439
00:22:40,959 --> 00:22:42,199
dan rasa malu nak
balik istana dan menghadap beta.

440
00:22:42,839 --> 00:22:43,680
Dia menulis kepada beta bahawa

441
00:22:44,160 --> 00:22:45,199
dia nak meletakkan jawatan.

442
00:22:45,839 --> 00:22:46,880
Dia masih muda,

443
00:22:46,880 --> 00:22:48,239
tapi rasa begitu hampa.

444
00:22:49,239 --> 00:22:50,280
Melalui kata-katanya,

445
00:22:50,800 --> 00:22:52,000
dia berniat nak mengelak
daripada hal ehwal duniawi.

446
00:22:53,359 --> 00:22:54,760
Rasa-rasanya, dia enggan balik.

447
00:22:57,040 --> 00:22:58,560
Dah beberapa hari saja.

448
00:22:59,239 --> 00:23:00,560
Pembantu kanan awak ini

449
00:23:00,959 --> 00:23:02,239
dah meninggalkan awak.

450
00:23:03,280 --> 00:23:04,560
Sudah pastinya tak baik.

451
00:23:09,560 --> 00:23:10,319
Tulis sepucuk surat.

452
00:23:10,760 --> 00:23:11,800
Suruh dia jangan pergi.

453
00:23:12,959 --> 00:23:13,760
Junjung kasih tuanku.

454
00:23:14,599 --> 00:23:15,479
Patik beredar dulu.

455
00:23:22,680 --> 00:23:23,719
(Tuanku pasti mengambil tahu bahawa)

456
00:23:24,199 --> 00:23:26,839
(patik, Fang Haishi
gagal memburu pembelot)

457
00:23:27,160 --> 00:23:28,400
(dan menghampakan jasa tuanku.)

458
00:23:28,880 --> 00:23:29,959
(Patik jatuh sakit lagi sekarang,)

459
00:23:30,119 --> 00:23:31,199
(jadi lagi tak guna.)

460
00:23:31,839 --> 00:23:32,319
(Maka,)

461
00:23:32,920 --> 00:23:34,959
(patik mohon perkenan tuanku)

462
00:23:35,400 --> 00:23:36,760
(untuk patik meletakkan jawatan.)

463
00:23:43,719 --> 00:23:44,160
Tuan besar.

464
00:24:38,620 --> 00:24:43,200
♪Dengan ciuman saya yang tanpa gangguan♪

465
00:24:43,800 --> 00:24:45,710
♪Dengan keikhlasan saya yang berlebihan
menenangkan hati kita♪

466
00:24:45,719 --> 00:24:47,319
Tok guru dah tercedera.

467
00:24:48,439 --> 00:24:49,119
Tok guru.

468
00:24:50,950 --> 00:24:52,880
♪Angin sejuk menghembus bulan,
tolak pintu besar♪

469
00:24:52,880 --> 00:24:53,719
Tok guru,

470
00:24:54,239 --> 00:24:55,470
biar saya tengok luka awak.

471
00:24:55,479 --> 00:24:56,770
♪Apa-apa pun tak tertinggal♪

472
00:24:58,079 --> 00:24:59,439
Parahnya luka tok guru.

473
00:24:59,719 --> 00:25:00,839
Saya sapu ubat untuk awak.

474
00:25:01,119 --> 00:25:02,839
Jika tok guru enggan bermain catur,

475
00:25:03,119 --> 00:25:04,760
apa kata bertaruh dengan Haishi?

476
00:25:05,199 --> 00:25:06,319
Tok guru, sila teka.

477
00:25:06,719 --> 00:25:08,319
Biji catur hitam ada pada tangan mana?

478
00:25:08,520 --> 00:25:09,880
Jika tok guru salah teka,

479
00:25:10,040 --> 00:25:11,119
maknanya saya menang.

480
00:25:11,520 --> 00:25:12,319
Jika saya menang,

481
00:25:12,479 --> 00:25:13,880
tok guru perlu menjanjikan satu perkara.

482
00:25:14,079 --> 00:25:14,959
Tak kira Haishi

483
00:25:15,160 --> 00:25:16,199
buat apa-apa yang salah selepas ini,

484
00:25:16,359 --> 00:25:17,760
tok guru boleh
memarahi dan menghukum saya,

485
00:25:17,920 --> 00:25:19,079
tapi jangan tak hiraukan saya.

486
00:25:20,479 --> 00:25:21,239
Tangan kanan.

487
00:25:22,439 --> 00:25:22,920
Saya dah menang.

488
00:25:23,719 --> 00:25:24,160
Janji,

489
00:25:24,319 --> 00:25:25,599
tok guru jangan tak hiraukan saya kelak.

490
00:25:26,359 --> 00:25:27,079
Tok guru mendidik Haishi

491
00:25:27,280 --> 00:25:28,040
sekian banyak tahun ini,

492
00:25:28,199 --> 00:25:29,560
Haishi ingatnya dalam hati

493
00:25:29,719 --> 00:25:30,520
dan amat berterima kasih

494
00:25:30,680 --> 00:25:31,560
atas bimbingan tok guru terhadap saya.

495
00:25:31,599 --> 00:25:32,079
Saya...

496
00:25:32,599 --> 00:25:34,040
Saya akan lagi berusaha kelak.

497
00:25:34,400 --> 00:25:34,880
Lagi...

498
00:25:35,280 --> 00:25:36,640
Lagipun...

499
00:25:36,800 --> 00:25:38,079
Lagipun, peperiksaan awam diraja
kali ini.

500
00:25:38,359 --> 00:25:38,760
Ya.

501
00:25:38,920 --> 00:25:40,359
Saya juga akan berusaha dalam
peperiksaan awam diraja.

502
00:25:41,920 --> 00:25:42,479
Saya...

503
